ActCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
SubjectCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation ** Premium Rate 2012-2013 **
PrecisOrder fixing at two ninths of one per cent the percentage used for the purpose of assessing the maximum Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation annual premium of each member institution for the premium year beginning on May 1, 2012 and ending on April 30, 2013.
